♪ So she rode away ♪

01:35:12.957 --> 01:35:14.874
♪ Just where, now is a mystery ♪

01:35:14.959 --> 01:35:17.335
♪ But Cat rode into history ♪

01:35:17.420 --> 01:35:20.714
♪ And her legend grew ♪

01:35:20.798 --> 01:35:23.925
♪ She was the queen
of the outlaws ♪

